# ==========================================
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# ==========================================
# 1. Replace YOUR_VPS_IP with actual IP address
# 2. OR replace yourdomain.com with your actual domain
# 3. Uncomment the configuration you want to use
# 4. Save and test: nginx -t
# 5. Reload: systemctl reload nginx
# ==========================================
